---
// Common-mode vs differential-mode radiation visualization
---
<div class="not-prose grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
  <figure class="rounded-lg border border-sky-200 bg-sky-50 p-3">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-sky-700">Differential-mode (DM) radiation</div>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 320 180" class="mt-2 w-full">
      <rect x="1" y="1" width="318" height="178" fill="#fff" stroke="#e2e8f0" />
      <!-- Source/load with two parallel traces -->
      <rect x="20" y="80" width="36" height="22" fill="#0f172a" />
      <text x="24" y="95" font-size="9" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">SRC</text>
      <rect x="244" y="80" width="36" height="22" fill="#0f172a" />
      <text x="248" y="95" font-size="9" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">RX</text>

      <!-- Two traces close together -->
      <line x1="56" y1="85"  x2="244" y2="85"  stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" />
      <line x1="56" y1="100" x2="244" y2="100" stroke="#0ea5e9" stroke-width="2" />

      <!-- Currents in opposite directions -->
      <text x="100" y="80" font-size="9" fill="#0369a1" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">→ I</text>
      <text x="100" y="113" font-size="9" fill="#0369a1" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">← I</text>

      <!-- Field cancellation indication -->
      <text x="150" y="135" font-size="10" fill="#10b981" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" text-anchor="middle">두 trace 의 필드가</text>
      <text x="150" y="148" font-size="10" fill="#10b981" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" text-anchor="middle">멀리서 거의 상쇄</text>
      <text x="150" y="166" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" text-anchor="middle">→ 방사 작음 (loop area 의 함수)</text>
    </svg>
    <figcaption class="mt-1 text-xs text-sky-800">차동 신호 — 두 트레이스를 가까이 두면 자기장이 멀리서 상쇄. <b>loop area 작을수록 방사 적음</b>.</figcaption>
  </figure>

  <figure class="rounded-lg border border-rose-200 bg-rose-50 p-3">
    <div class="font-mono text-xs text-rose-700">Common-mode (CM) radiation</div>
    <svg viewBox="0 0 320 180" class="mt-2 w-full">
      <rect x="1" y="1" width="318" height="178" fill="#fff" stroke="#e2e8f0" />
      <rect x="20" y="80" width="36" height="22" fill="#0f172a" />
      <text x="24" y="95" font-size="9" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">SRC</text>
      <rect x="244" y="80" width="36" height="22" fill="#0f172a" />
      <text x="248" y="95" font-size="9" fill="#fff" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">RX</text>

      <!-- Cable -->
      <line x1="56" y1="85"  x2="244" y2="85"  stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="2" />
      <line x1="56" y1="100" x2="244" y2="100" stroke="#dc2626" stroke-width="2" />

      <!-- Currents in same direction (CM) -->
      <text x="100" y="80" font-size="9" fill="#9f1239" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">→ I_cm</text>
      <text x="100" y="113" font-size="9" fill="#9f1239" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace">→ I_cm</text>

      <!-- Cable acting as antenna -->
      <path d="M 70 30 Q 150 10 230 30" fill="none" stroke="#fbbf24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-dasharray="3 2" />
      <text x="150" y="42" font-size="9" fill="#a16207" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" text-anchor="middle">전체 케이블 = 안테나</text>

      <text x="150" y="135" font-size="10" fill="#dc2626" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" text-anchor="middle">두 trace 같은 방향 →</text>
      <text x="150" y="148" font-size="10" fill="#dc2626" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" text-anchor="middle">필드 더해짐 (안 상쇄)</text>
      <text x="150" y="166" font-size="9" fill="#94a3b8" font-family="ui-monospace, monospace" text-anchor="middle">→ <b>방사 매우 큼</b> (cable 길이 의존)</text>
    </svg>
    <figcaption class="mt-1 text-xs text-rose-800">공통모드 — 두 트레이스에 같은 방향 잡음. 매우 작아도 (μA 급) 큰 방사. EMI 시험 fail 의 80% 가 공통모드.</figcaption>
  </figure>
</div>
